        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/skunk/scene_skunk.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 88e277b3-9bf8-4032-9985-113dec131436).Image",
        "Description": "Good afternoon, 47.\r\rOur client has hired us to kill three targets in the suburban town of Whittleton Creek, USA, perferably with the use of a knife.\r\rYour first targets are Hollis Mack, a supposed garbage man, Susan Wilson, the host of a garden party happening today, and mailman Dale Anderson.\r\rThe client, whoever they may be, was very specific when it came to this contract. Silent Assasin, Suit Only, 47. And you only have a small window to do so.\r\rGood luck, 47.",
